Don't become discouraged and do your best to assume that your partner is not deliberately trying to upset you. Often what is behind arguing and miscommunication is unmet needs. When we don't feel heard or valued it can trigger all sorts of emotions. \
Another aspect to relationships that is key is your attachment style and you can find the attachment style questionnaire on Cowch to help you understand your own vulnerabilities in the relationship. There are four attachment styles and they are formed during childhood.\
Secure attachment style\
Anxious attachment style\
Avoidant attachment style\
Disorganised attachment style\
Take the questionnaire to figure out your attachment style and this will help you prevent some of the behaviours that might be interfering in your relationship.\
